🌸 FLOWER ECOMMERCE
WEBSITE CONTENT BIBLE
Complete Copy, Categories, Products & Policy Content

Built for a Nairobi-based luxury flower delivery brand
Researched & Compiled by Claude · May 2026
 
How to Use This Document
This document contains every piece of copy, every product description, every policy, and every category name you need to launch your flower ecommerce website. It is organised page-by-page and section-by-section so you can simply copy and paste into your website builder (WooCommerce, Shopify, etc.).
Each section is labelled with the page it belongs to, what element it is (headline, subheading, body copy, button text, etc.), and any notes on where to place it. You do not need to use every word verbatim — treat this as your starting draft and personalise with your actual brand name, pricing, and photos.
Pages covered in this document:
•	Homepage (Hero, Trust Bar, Categories, Products, Testimonials, etc.)
•	Shop / Category pages
•	Individual Product pages — 20 sample product listings
•	About Us page
•	Contact Us page
•	Delivery & Shipping Information page
•	FAQ page
•	Refund & Returns Policy page
•	Blog post ideas + 3 sample blog post outlines
•	Checkout copy (cart, order confirmation emails)
•	WhatsApp / social media captions
•	SEO — meta titles & descriptions for all pages

 
