PAGE 2 — PRODUCT LISTINGS
Below are 20 complete product listings. Each one includes a product name, category, short description (used in grid cards), long description (used on the product page), suggested pricing tiers, and add-on options.
💡 NOTE: Replace [PRICE] with your actual prices in KES. Photos should be professional, well-lit, and show the arrangement from multiple angles.

Product 1 — Classic Red Roses Bouquet
Category	Romance & Love / Birthday / Anniversary
Short Description	Twelve long-stem red roses — the timeless declaration of love.
Badge	Best Seller
Sizes & Prices	6 stems — KES [PRICE]  |  12 stems — KES [PRICE]  |  24 stems — KES [PRICE]
Add-ons	Vase (+KES 500), Chocolates (+KES 800), Greeting Card (+KES 200), Teddy Bear (+KES 1,200)

Long Description (for Product Page):
There is no bouquet more iconic than a dozen red roses. Our Classic Red Roses Bouquet features hand-selected, long-stem roses with deep velvet petals — each one chosen for its perfect bloom and vivid colour. Wrapped in premium tissue and tied with satin ribbon, this arrangement is a timeless way to say 'I love you' to someone truly special.
Red roses carry centuries of meaning: passion, devotion, and deep romantic love. Whether for Valentine's Day, an anniversary, or a spontaneous gesture that takes her breath away — this bouquet never misses.
Care Instructions:
Trim stems at a 45° angle. Place in fresh water in a clean vase. Keep away from direct sunlight and fruits. Change water every 2 days. Flowers will stay fresh for 5–7 days.

Product 2 — Sunshine Yellow Sunflowers
Category	Birthday / Congratulations / Just Because
Short Description	Bold, bright, and bursting with joy — sunflowers that make any room glow.
Badge	Customer Favourite
Sizes & Prices	5 stems — KES [PRICE]  |  10 stems — KES [PRICE]  |  15 stems — KES [PRICE]
Add-ons	Vase (+KES 500), Balloon (+KES 400), Greeting Card (+KES 200)

Long Description:
Sunflowers are the happiest flowers on earth — and our Sunshine Yellow Sunflower bouquet captures that joy perfectly. Each stem stands tall, crowned with a full, golden bloom that radiates warmth and positivity. Wrapped in natural kraft paper with a rustic twine bow, this arrangement is pure, uncomplicated happiness.
Sunflowers symbolise loyalty, longevity, and adoration — making them ideal for birthdays, 'congratulations', or a simple 'I'm thinking of you.' These are pet-friendly and make a stunning centrepiece in any home.
Care Instructions:
Sunflowers love sunlight. Place near a window and change water daily. Trim stems every 2 days for maximum vase life of 7–10 days.

Product 3 — Blush Peonies & Garden Roses
Category	Romance / Wedding / Anniversary / Birthday
Short Description	Soft, romantic, and utterly luxurious — peonies and garden roses in full bloom.
Badge	Luxury Collection
Sizes & Prices	Small — KES [PRICE]  |  Medium — KES [PRICE]  |  Large — KES [PRICE]
Add-ons	Premium Vase (+KES 1,200), Chocolates (+KES 800), Personalized Card (+KES 200)

Long Description:
Nothing captures the spirit of romance and femininity like a bouquet of full-bloom peonies and garden roses. This arrangement features layers of soft blush tones — from pale cream to dusky pink — with lush, ruffled petals that practically overflow with beauty.
Peonies symbolise prosperity, romance, and good fortune. Paired with garden roses (which represent admiration and grace), this bouquet is the perfect gift for weddings, anniversaries, or anytime you want to make someone feel truly cherished. Available in our small, medium, and large sizes to suit your occasion and budget.
Care Instructions:
Place in cool water immediately upon arrival. Keep away from direct heat. Peonies will continue to open over 2–3 days. Vase life: 5–7 days.

Product 4 — White Lily Elegance
Category	Sympathy / Wedding / Get Well / Congratulations
Short Description	Pure, serene, and deeply graceful — white lilies for life's most meaningful moments.
Badge	New Arrival
Sizes & Prices	3 stems — KES [PRICE]  |  6 stems — KES [PRICE]  |  9 stems — KES [PRICE]
Add-ons	Vase (+KES 500), Ribbon Upgrade (+KES 300), Greeting Card (+KES 200)

Long Description:
White lilies are among the most meaningful flowers in the world. Each stem carries multiple blooms that open sequentially, extending the beauty of your gift over several days. With their signature fragrance and pristine white petals, they communicate elegance, renewal, and heartfelt sincerity.
These are ideal for sympathy arrangements, hospital visits, wedding ceremonies, or any occasion where you want to express deep respect and care. Our White Lily Elegance bouquet is arranged in premium tissue with a satin bow — understated luxury at its finest.
Care Instructions:
Remove any leaves that will sit below the waterline. Add flower food to vase water. Trim stems at an angle every 2–3 days. Vase life: 10–14 days as buds continue to open.

Product 5 — Tropical Paradise Mix
Category	Birthday / Congratulations / Corporate / Just Because
Short Description	Bold tropicals and exotic blooms — a vibrant Nairobi statement bouquet.
Badge	Kenya Special
Sizes & Prices	Medium — KES [PRICE]  |  Large — KES [PRICE]
Add-ons	Vase (+KES 600), Greeting Card (+KES 200)

Long Description:
Inspired by the colours and energy of East Africa, our Tropical Paradise Mix is a celebration of bold, exotic beauty. This arrangement features a hand-selected mix of anthuriums, proteas, bird-of-paradise, and seasonal tropical foliage — all sourced from local Kenyan flower farms.
Vibrant, long-lasting, and unlike any ordinary bouquet, this is the gift for people who love standing out. Perfect for corporate events, milestone birthdays, or as a show-stopping table centrepiece.
Care Instructions:
Tropical flowers are hardy and long-lasting. Change water every 3 days. Keep in a bright, well-lit area out of direct sunlight. Vase life: 10–14 days.

