PAGE 3 — ABOUT US
💡 NOTE: The About Us page builds trust and connection. Use real photos of your team, your studio, and your process.

Page Title
Our Story — Flowers with Heart

Hero / Opening Paragraph
At [Brand Name], we believe flowers are more than a gift — they are a feeling. Every bouquet we arrange carries a piece of our heart, crafted with care for the moments that matter most in your life.
Founded in Nairobi, we started with a simple mission: to make the finest, freshest flowers accessible to every person in our city — from a last-minute birthday surprise to an elaborate wedding installation.

Our Story Section
Heading:
How It All Began
[Brand Name] was born out of a love for beautiful things and a deep desire to bring joy to people's everyday lives. What started as a small flower stall has grown into Nairobi's trusted premium flower delivery service — but our values have never changed: freshness, quality, and genuine care for every customer.
We source our flowers every morning — from local Kenyan farms in the Rift Valley and from carefully selected international growers. Every stem is inspected, every arrangement is hand-crafted, and every delivery is made with pride.

Our Values Section
Heading:
What We Stand For
•	Freshness First — We never sell day-old flowers. Our stock is sourced fresh every morning.
•	Craftsmanship — Every arrangement is designed by our trained floral artisans.
•	Reliability — When we say same-day delivery, we mean it. Every time.
•	Sustainability — We use eco-friendly packaging and support sustainable farming practices.
•	Customer Joy — Your satisfaction is not just a policy — it is the reason we wake up every morning.

